abstract_str: pc adam __rushton__ accused of having sex with four women while on duty . one woman said they met after she reported burglary and stayed in touch . she said they had sex four or five times and once he turned up in uniform . woman , then 21 , claimed __rushton__ also asked her to text him ` some filth ' said she stayed in touch with ` nice police officer ' in case she needed help . __rushton__ denies committing 10 charges of misconduct in a public office . he also pleaded not guilty to obtaining personal data without permission .
